shoes made of emeralds, malachites, lapis lazulis and moss. because they are only virtual, these shoes did not generate any mining process, exploitation of natural resources or the exploitation of poorly paid human labor. it is also a joke about how uncomfortable these shoes would be if they were actually worn, as they would be too heavy and hard. also, c'est si ne pas une shoes.
